    GetElementsOperation<EntitySeed,CloseableIterable<EntitySeed>>, GetIterableElementsOperation<EntitySeed,EntitySeed>, GetIterableOperation<EntitySeed,EntitySeed>, GetOperation<EntitySeed,CloseableIterable<EntitySeed>>, Operation<CloseableIterable<EntitySeed>,CloseableIterable<EntitySeed>>

    public class GetAdjacentEntitySeeds
extends AbstractGetIterableElementsOperation<EntitySeed,EntitySeed>
    An GetAdjacentEntitySeeds operation will return the EntitySeeds at the opposite end of connected edges to a seed EntitySeed. Seed matching is always RELATED.
    See Also:
    GetAdjacentEntitySeeds.Builder, GetOperation
